author: dims
msg: Fix for Bug 21510 - call timeout when using SAAJ
SOAPConnectionImpl exposes timeout. So you can typecast SOAPConnection to SOAPConnectionImpl and use the set/get timeout methods.

author: dims
msg: Fix for Bug 21470 - Custom Exceptions kill Document style service WSDL creation
- Inform user if they have not registered a typemapping/beanmapping for the exception
- Use the interface namespace for the exception.
